trans-unit.source: Enables using a number of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] models as a unit.
trans-unit.target: Gjør det mulig å bruke en rekke [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] modeller som en enhet.

trans-unit.source: Model3DGroup allows a developer to apply transformations, animations, or other processes to a group of [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] models as though they were a single model.
trans-unit.target: Model3DGroup gjør det mulig for utviklere å bruke transformasjoner, animasjoner eller andre prosesser til en gruppe [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] modeller som om de var en enkelt modell.
